This app is a simple app to combine some tutorials and display some of the technologies we us.

Things in here:

1) The DJango Tutorial with some goodness added.
2) Tastypie tutorial plus more.
3) Using unit tests with Django and Tastypie
4) A simple tutorial (not from another site/tech) that show's how to
  a) Use our Multi-authentication to create and access a Tastypie REST API